│  ▶│ This will permanently delete the vault at                            │   │
│   │ /home/u/.local/share/paladin-auth/vault.bin and its backup at        │   │
│   │ /home/u/.local/share/paladin-auth/vault.bin.bak. This cannot be      │   │
│  ↑│ undone. The files are unlinked, not securely erased, so an encrypted │   │
